---
description: "Work Packets"
globs: ["**/*.md", "**/*.toml", "**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx", "**/*.js", "**/*.jsx", "**/*.py"]
alwaysApply: false
---

When asked to split work across tools/models or make a plan parallelizable, produce compact Execution Packets: objective, owner fit, scope, dependencies, and acceptance evidence. For UI-heavy work without settled visual direction, run Design Inspiration Flow before final implementation packets. Use Prompt Contracts only for delegation-ready handoffs.
